# FlexFlow — Kinetic Pastel Design

Full spec: [`design/DESIGN.md`](../../DESIGN.md). Flutter tokens live in `lib/theme/`; shared widgets in `lib/widgets/`.

## Brand

Optimistic, soft-tactile fitness UI. Candy-coated pastels, heavy whitespace, oversized pill controls, squishy tap feedback. **Not** hardcore gym aesthetics.

## Never hardcode design values

```dart
// ✅ GOOD
padding: const EdgeInsets.all(AppSpacing.gutter),
style: AppTextStyles.headlineMd,
color: AppColors.primary,
borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppRadius.card),

// ❌ BAD
padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),
style: TextStyle(fontSize: 24, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold),
color: Color(0xFF006C52),
```

Use `AppColors`, `AppTextStyles`, `AppSpacing`, `AppRadius`, and `AppTheme.light()` / `AppTheme.dark()`.

## Typography

- **Plus Jakarta Sans** — display, headlines, labels, stat numbers
- **Be Vietnam Pro** — body copy
- Weights/reps/times/duration **must** use `AppTextStyles.statNumber`, never body styles
- App bar brand: `headlineMd` ~22px in `AppColors.primary`

## Color semantics

| Role | Use |
|------|-----|
| `primary` (Mint) | Go actions, start/finish, brand accent |
| `primaryContainer` | Cardio cards, nav active pill |
| `secondaryContainer` | Strength cards, chips, toggle off |
| `tertiaryContainer` | Rest timers, yoga, alerts |
| `surfaceContainerLowest` | Cards, list rows |

**Category mapping:** Gym → `secondaryContainer` · Cardio → `primaryContainer` · Yoga → `tertiaryContainer`

## Shape & spacing

- Base unit: **8px** — all spacing via `AppSpacing`
- **Pills everywhere** — buttons, chips, nav active state (`AppRadius.pill`)
- Cards: `AppRadius.card` (24px). Inputs/set rows: `AppRadius.md` (16px)
- Touch targets: 48px min, 64px for primary actions

## Interaction

- Wrap tappable elements in **`Squish`** (scale 0.96–0.98 on press) — never shadow-based press states
- Tonal surface shifts for depth; shadows only on FAB / finish button / occasional hover
- Glassmorphism **only** on `FlexTopBar` and `FlexBottomNav` (20px blur, 85% opacity)

## Shared components — reuse before reinventing

| Widget | Use |
|--------|-----|
| `Squish` | All interactive press feedback |
| `PrimaryPillButton` | Primary/secondary CTAs |
| `CategoryPill` | Muscle groups, workout tags |
| `FlexTopBar` | Shell top chrome |
| `FlexBottomNav` | Shell bottom nav (4 tabs) |

## Screen rules

- **Shell screens** (Workouts, Calendar, Progress, Settings): `FlexTopBar` + `FlexBottomNav` in `HomeShell`
- **Active session**: contextual header (pause · title + timer · settings); bottom nav **replaced** by Add Note + Finish Workout bar
- **Splash**: gradient mesh, floating icon, `displayLgMobile` wordmark
- Scrollable bodies need bottom padding to clear FAB/nav bar

## Do / don't summary

- ✅ Material 3 color roles via `AppColors`
- ✅ `google_fonts` via `AppTextStyles` (already configured)
- ✅ Private widget classes for screen sections (`_Header`, `_SetRow`)
- ❌ Inline `Color(...)`, raw `TextStyle`, magic-number padding/radii
- ❌ Sharp corners on buttons or cards
- ❌ Drop shadows as default press/active feedback
